755
01:07:34,560 --> 01:07:36,060
How far in do you estimate it to be?

756
01:07:36,160 --> 01:07:39,660
Oh I'd ah, I'd say, about
a quarter of a mile from this end.

757
01:07:40,060 --> 01:07:41,860
That puts the Mantis
below the water line.

758
01:07:42,360 --> 01:07:44,260
